relation: Here is an FX editor for Super Metroid. Don’t forget to run the language change program to use in English.

Here is a utility that allows you to tweak with some of the settings in Super Metroid. Before running this program be sure to run the language selector to change it to English for those who do not read Japanese.

An editor for Super Metroid coded in VB with some C dll’s. Lots of bug fixes, tweaks, and a bit more streamlined than before. Translation files for English, French, Finnish, and Latin. Plugins are now supported.
